"1 1/2 lb. fresh green beans, trimmed","2 cups multi-colored grape tomatoes","2 Tbsp. olive oil","1 1/2 tsp.  kosher salt","1 tsp. black pepper","2  (12 to 16-oz.) boneless rib-eye steaks (about 1 1/4-in. thick)","3 Tbsp.  unsalted butter, softened","1 1/2 Tbsp.  crumbled blue cheese","1/2 tsp.  chopped fresh thyme"